    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-11-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="628" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d628">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 16,
                                    1895</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>To cooperate with the six Powers in any necessary measures to stop the
                            general massacre. Have avoided and will avoid all conferences regarding
                            such measures until you distinctly instruct otherwise. Russia has only
                            one gunboat on southern coast of the Black Sea, now at Trebizond.
                            Russian ambassador says others will be sent if massacres renewed on the
                            coast of the Black Sea.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
